{"tid":1390200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯國譴責俄對示威者濫用武力","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:11:16.000Z","uid":55951,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"117957a80c99e7c113321bcfad9d131754c0b90f","tid":1390200,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】聯合國周二（30日）譴責俄羅斯警方在上周六（27日）的莫斯科示威中，使用過度武力對待示威者，造成逾70人受傷。人權事務高級專員發言人科爾維爾（Rupert Colville）表示，警方使用武力需與遇到的威脅相對稱，而且武力亦應該是最後手段，又呼籲俄方應允許民眾在不受限制的情况下組織及參與和平集會。<br />\n<br />\n俄國當局指控57名反對派或獨立候選人偽造選民簽名，禁止他們參與9月莫斯科市議會選舉，觸發上周六的示威，警方在行動中拘捕逾1400人。科爾維爾質疑當局取消候選人資格的決定。反對派呼籲周六再度示威，俄羅斯第一副總檢察官布克曼（Alexander Buksman）同日警告：「檢察官應以嚴厲方式，阻止組織及參加者在非法和未經批准的公眾集會採取行動。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190731/s00014/1564511513039/%e8%81%af%e5%9c%8b%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e4%bf%84%e5%b0%8d%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e6%bf%ab%e7%94%a8%e6%ad%a6%e5%8a%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00014%2F1564511513039%2F%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e4%25bf%2584%25e5%25b0%258d%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%25bf%25ab%25e7%2594%25a8%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%258a%259b&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qncwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=3659e268\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190731%2Fs00014%2F1564511513039%2F%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac%25e4%25bf%2584%25e5%25b0%258d%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e6%25bf%25ab%25e7%2594%25a8%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e5%258a%259b&h=c352c29f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190731/s00014/1564511513039/%e8%81%af%e5%9c%8b%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e4%bf%84%e5%b0%8d%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e6%bf%ab%e7%94%a8%e6%ad%a6%e5%8a%9b</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DgmZ