\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/hWh5Sax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWh5Sax.jpg&h=f682f165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9db3ca4a7ce8fb375be52831dd0c5ca0d3fb2991","tid":1390200,"uid":55951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:56:26.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾聯合國淨係識奶中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae693461ff1431dd07b5865fcbafad564a9d62a","tid":1390200,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"中共同俄佬搞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8916e5fd9f3a3c1b4fe39eb84047ae2a5f4d9fad","tid":1390200,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f71cfb64631f96b951be0a11fc92f6fea8f8bdee","tid":1390200,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解香港冇事?!"},{"pid":"15119b125862a1cfd24eafa72d0555734193a34b","tid":1390200,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"咀炮就叻"},{"pid":"712400c452bc7946eaa85066f3dca381b265731b","tid":1390